Package implementations

Class BSTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>>

java.lang.Object
implementations.BSTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - The type of elements stored in the BST, which must be comparable.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, BSTreeADT<E>
public class BSTree<E extends Comparable<? super E>> extends Object implements BSTreeADT<E>
Implementation of a Binary Search Tree (BST) that implements BSTreeADT interface. The tree maintains elements in sorted order and provides traversal methods.
